"\n"
"\n"
"Ongeldige spelersnaam opgegeven.\n"
"Controleer je profiel en probeer het opnieuw."

#: Sources/Main.cpp:1182
msgid ""
"\f[c:#704a4a]Cannot connect to the server!\f[/c]\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"This client is not in the server whitelist.\n"
"Contact server administrators for more information."
msgstr ""
"\f[c:#704a4a]Kan geen verbinding maken met de server!\f[/c]\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Deze client staat niet op de server-whitelist.\n"
"Neem contact op met de serverbeheerders voor meer informatie."

#: Sources/Main.cpp:1183
msgid ""
"\f[c:#704a4a]Cannot connect to the server!\f[/c]\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Server requires 3rd party authentication provider.\n"
"Contact server administrators for more information."
